text: The White Eagle () is a 1928 Soviet silent drama movie directed by Yakov Protazanov.Белый орелАфиша It stars Vasili Kachalov, Anna Sten, and Vsevolod Meyerhold. ==Actors== * Vasili Kachalov as Governor * Anna Sten as Governor's wife * Vsevolod Meyerhold as Dignitary * Ivan Chuvelyov * Andrey Petrovsky as Chief of Police == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Russian silent movies Category:Russian drama movies Category:1928 drama movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by Yakov Protazanov Category:Soviet drama movies
title: The White Eagle
